The paper discusses a novel method for channel estimation in mmWave communication, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The focus on positioning and mapping also suggests a potential fit with systems and control (cs.SY). The use of multipath signals and simulation results suggest a potential fit with multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV).
